833
00:22:11,732 --> 00:22:13,400
Adrien!

834
00:22:13,467 --> 00:22:14,868
Ouf... Ouf...

835
00:22:14,935 --> 00:22:16,136
- Qu'est-ce qui se passe,

836
00:22:16,203 --> 00:22:17,404
Marinette?

837
00:22:17,471 --> 00:22:18,672
- J'ai... Je suis

838
00:22:18,739 --> 00:22:19,940
