847
00:22:30,050 --> 00:22:32,319
- Hum?

848
00:22:32,386 --> 00:22:35,589
- Adrien, je t'aime.

849
00:22:37,157 --> 00:22:38,492
- Tu ne pouvais pas faire

850
00:22:38,559 --> 00:22:40,561
