851
00:22:40,894 --> 00:22:43,063
(musique sentimentale)

852
00:22:43,130 --> 00:22:46,633
- Adrien, non.

853
00:22:47,634 --> 00:22:49,736
- Oh!

854
00:22:49,803 --> 00:22:52,005
- Quelque chose ne va pas?

855
00:22:52,072 --> 00:22:53,273
- Je ne sais pas,

856
00:22:53,340 --> 00:22:54,608
