857
00:22:54,675 --> 00:22:56,643
Tu devrais peut-être rentrer.

858
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:59,346
- Oh... D'accord...

859
00:22:59,413 --> 00:23:00,000
- Excuse-moi.

860
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,448
- Excuse-moi.

861
00:23:04,451 --> 00:23:07,454
